AT&T Free Msg:  Stream Saver has now been added to eligible lines with qualified plans on your account. Stream Saver allows you to save data by streaming higher definition video at Standard Definition quality (about 480p.)  Call 611 or log onto your myAT&T app to turn it off or back on anytime. Please note:  For Stream Saver to take effect on new lines or numbers added after December 13, 2016, you need to use myAT&T to turn it off and back on, wait 5 minutes and then restart your device.  For more info visit att.com/ssinfo  If you recently changed your plan to Unlimited Choice, please disregard.
